    "13 Without engaging in an exhaustive search of different prompts, we included five prompts with increasing effort focused on generating diverse responses.",
    "We report the prompts used in Table 2.",
    "These begin with a simple query asking in a straightforward manner, then add the word \"diverse\" in prompt 2, then ask for \"as many diverse... as possible.\"",
    "While most of the responses to these initial prompts include lists, prompts 4 and 5 specifically ask for the LLM for a list of twenty responses in order to encourage the idea of going beyond the most common responses.",
    "Finally, prompt five"
